comment:
* Provides a convenient way to set the fields of a {@link NetworkRegistrationInfo} when * creating a new instance. * *

The example below shows how you might create a new {@code NetworkRegistrationInfo}: * * 


     *
     * NetworkRegistrationInfo nri = new NetworkRegistrationInfo.Builder()
     *     .setAccessNetworkTechnology(TelephonyManager.NETWORK_TYPE_LTE)
     *     .setRegistrationState(REGISTRATION_STATE_HOME)
     *     .build();
     *
* @hide

methods.name: public Builder setDomain(@Domain int domain)
methods.comment:
* Set the network domain.
         *
         * @param domain Network domain.
         *
         * @return The same instance of the builder.

methods.name: public Builder setTransportType(@TransportType int transportType)
methods.comment:
* Set the transport type.
         *
         * @param transportType Transport type.
         *
         * @return The same instance of the builder.

methods.name: public Builder setRegistrationState(@RegistrationState int registrationState)
methods.comment:
* Set the registration state.
         *
         * @param registrationState The registration state.
         *
         * @return The same instance of the builder.

methods.name: public Builder setAccessNetworkTechnology(@NetworkType int accessNetworkTechnology)
methods.comment:
* Set tne access network technology.
         *
         * @return The same instance of the builder.
         *
         * @param accessNetworkTechnology The access network technology

methods.name: public Builder setRejectCause(int rejectCause)
methods.comment:
* Set the network reject cause.
         *
         * @param rejectCause Reason for denial if the registration state is
         * {@link #REGISTRATION_STATE_DENIED}.Depending on {@code accessNetworkTechnology}, the
         * values are defined in 3GPP TS 24.008 10.5.3.6 for UMTS, 3GPP TS 24.301 9.9.3.9 for LTE,
         * and 3GPP2 A.S0001 6.2.2.44 for CDMA. If the reject cause is not supported or unknown, set
         * it to 0.
         *
         * @return The same instance of the builder.

methods.name: public Builder setEmergencyOnly(boolean emergencyOnly)
methods.comment:
* Set emergency only.
         *
         * @param emergencyOnly True if this network registration is for emergency use only.
         *
         * @return The same instance of the builder.
         * @hide

methods.name: public Builder setAvailableServices(@NonNull @ServiceType List<Integer> availableServices)
methods.comment:
* Set the available services.
         *
         * @param availableServices Available services.
         *
         * @return The same instance of the builder.
         * @hide

methods.name: public Builder setCellIdentity(@Nullable CellIdentity cellIdentity)
methods.comment:
* Set the cell identity.
         *
         * @param cellIdentity The cell identity.
         *
         * @return The same instance of the builder.
         * @hide

methods.name: public Builder setRegisteredPlmn(@Nullable String rplmn)
methods.comment:
* Set the registered PLMN.
         *
         * @param rplmn the registered plmn.
         *
         * @return The same instance of the builder.

methods.name: public Builder setVoiceSpecificInfo(@NonNull VoiceSpecificRegistrationInfo info)
methods.comment:
* Set voice specific registration information.
         *
         * @param info The voice specific registration information.
         * @return The builder.
         * @hide

methods.name: public Builder setDataSpecificInfo(@NonNull DataSpecificRegistrationInfo info)
methods.comment:
* Set data specific registration information.
         *
         * @param info The data specific registration information.
         * @return The builder.
         * @hide

methods.name: public Builder setIsNonTerrestrialNetwork(boolean isNonTerrestrialNetwork)
methods.comment:
* Set whether the network is a non-terrestrial network.
         *
         * @param isNonTerrestrialNetwork {@code true} if network is a non-terrestrial network
         *                                            else {@code false}.
         * @return The builder.

methods.name: public NetworkRegistrationInfo build()
methods.comment:
* Build the NetworkRegistrationInfo.
         * @return the NetworkRegistrationInfo object.
         * @hide
